comment:
Wow..I'm almost speechless.¬†


First thought, the level of grandiose here is probably at an all time high. I don't think I've ever seen someone's level of self importance so bloody high that they believe their opinion on another's choices is their business, and their right to not only formulate strong opinions on, especially in this context, but also and more importantly that they believe that they should make a video, addressing this person.¬†


What sort of insecurity & psychological obstacle is it that you hold, Kurtz? I'm genuinely asking because this right here seems to be impulsive and it has potential in backfiring on you.¬†

You are beyond in need for a self evaluation. And I don't mean any disrespect.¬†


I'm worried about your focus, well being and the status of the health in your marriage? Is he away from home alot? Do you feel alone in your views and you need to be heard? Is this why you're always posting your videos far too many times everyday?¬†

I have to tell you that doing that doesn't make any difference. Besides why do you need a bigger audience so badly? Why do you feel like not enough people agree with you?¬†

Or maybe it is that you don't feel like enough people disagree with you?¬†


I'm thinking it's a combination of both dependening on your mood. Your audience is there for you, to confirm your thinking is normal and to judge how many it seems to "upset people" feeds your need tor the boredom in your life.¬†

And the fact that your husband probably cannot stand any of this subject.¬†


Your YouTube audience supports your obsession on all of this. You can tell.¬†


Girl, I'm warning you now, you're digging a hole. Nobody needs to know your opinion on their life that you are misled to believe you know anything about.¬†


I want to hear you speak on the human flaws of your own life instead. Show us something real. Show us something human and vulnerable and that has the possibility of you losing your audience.¬†

Do something brave and bold.¬†

This isn't it. This is honestly and extremely uncreative, rude, arrogant and pompous.¬†


Like Elon Musk is going to even consider to condescend to humor you.¬†
